Figure 8. mD369G mutation reduces the flexibility of the AC region in molecular dynamics simulations (A) RMS fluctuation of Cα’s in the AC region obtained from molecular dynamics simulations of WT and D369A, E, G, N, P and W. Color shades indicate the structural motifs in the AC region, the dynamics of which are significantly affected by mD369G. (B) Motion of the WT (top) and mD369G (bottom) AC regions along the principal eigenvector from minima to maxima. Color codes are the same as in (A).

